                        <date>Mid-17th - mid-18th century (?)</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipit of Texts I-III; initial lines
                           of section of Text I; titles of books to be read; titles or initial lines
                           of prayers; some words: halle luya (fols.), bǝḍuʿ (fols. 37r), fǝtuḥa;
                           elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numbers.
 On
                           the incipit page of Texts I and III (fols. 1r and 61v) and on fol. 28r, a
                           few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
